  "version": "1.0.9",
  "apkUrl": "https://github.com/4d3l/dunes-updates/releases/download/v1.0.9/dunes_v1.0.9_relay_fix.apk",
  "releaseNotes": "🔴 Relay zombie loop	Added isConnecting ref — skips duplicate connectRelay calls while a socket is already connecting. Added allHeartbeatTimers Set — clears all timers on reconnect, not just the last one. Fixed heartbeat to only reconnect on readyState === 3 (CLOSED), not 0 (CONNECTING).
🔴 Dependency chain	closeVoicePc now uses localAudioStreamRef.current (stable ref) instead of localAudioStream (state), breaking the rebuild chain → handleIncomingSignal → connectRelay.
🌐 TURN servers	Replaced openrelay.metered.ca → global.relay.metered.ca with TCP fallback + Cloudflare STUN + iceCandidatePoolSize: 4 for both data and voice connections.
📍 IP + Flag	Settings → NETWORK now shows your public IP and country flag (e.g. 203.x.x.x · United Arab Emirates 🇦🇪).
🔔 Ringtone	Incoming calls now play a bundled ringtone MP3 + vibration pattern. Stops automatically on answer/reject.
⚙️ Tone picker	Settings → NETWORK → "Notification & Ringtone Sounds" opens Android's native OS sound picker for Dunes' notification channel.
"
}
